data.description: IMPRESSIVE! Check out this gorgeous, like new 3bd 2ba home with tons of living space! Stylish finishes complimented w/ upgrades makes this place truly turn key. Interior features: Spacious living room w/ vaulted ceiling and bay window with beautiful LVP flooring that continue throughout the kitchen, breakfast room and hallway. Superb kitchen with white cabinets, tile backsplash, granite tops, quality stainless appliances & stylish lighting! HUGE Master bedroom suite with walk in closet, custom tile in bath, separate shower, and dual sinks. Additional bedrooms offer plush carpet and a full bath. The LL is ready to be finished to add even more living space! Relax on your outside covered deck. Home is clean, bright and in great subdivision!
